"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T06:58:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇試過番大陸唱仁K? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食過學生妹&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">得咁乍？？？點信你真係政協呢？？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我識人識人..係政挾，北京上海學院／名中學任揀做陪月，愈高權力愈多P咁囉！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1297554cfcbb60b9bd37a011abc723bdfd335db2","tid":1092771,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7415a556cd5b515b046e0909b177d9976606524e","tid":1092771,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T06:44:54.000Z","msg":"你個女好好屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T07:18:46.000Z","msg":"佢健康有問題"},{"pid":"f59edcc0d286d8e019753f8ab95a0c5303d89019","tid":1092771,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T07:39:12.000Z","msg":"自貼thx"},{"pid":"ee97ec407a084a9bb65e9275229d9d5ac3f94d8b","tid":1092771,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f59edcc0d286d8e019753f8ab95a0c5303d89019","tid":1092771,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T07:39:12.000Z","msg":"自貼thx"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T14:54:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}